### Ascend API — Notifications
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT

### Get notifications (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get unread notification count
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get unread notifications only
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?unreadOnly=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Mark a single notification as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/NOTIFICATION_UUID/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Mark all notifications as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Delete a notification
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notifications/NOTIFICATION_UUID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
